text: The Annam flying frog, Daban flying frog, or Annam tree frog (Rhacophorus annamensis) is a frog. It lives in the Annamite Mountains in Vietnam and Cambodia. People think it might also live nearby in Laos. People have seen it between 700 and 1200 meters above sea level. ==References== Category:Frogs of Asia
title: Rhacophorus annamensis
